# ===================================
# INSTRUCTIONS FOR CUSTOMIZATION
# ===================================
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local in your project root
# 2. Update all values to match your hub's information
# 3. Uncomment Firebase variables if you're using Firebase
# 4. Replace placeholder URLs with your actual links
# 5. Update social media handles and contact information
# 6. Customize branding paths to point to your logo files
# 7. Set up your Google Calendar embed URL with your hub's calendar
# 8. Configure your Notion workspace URL for hub members
# 9. Update team allocations document URL
# 10. Test all links and ensure they work correctly

# Note: Environment variables starting with NEXT_PUBLIC_ are exposed to the browser
# Keep sensitive information in server-side only variables (without NEXT_PUBLIC_)

